{
  "stem": "25348.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews were rounded up in Luck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we, my mother and I and the 13 occupants of that ghetto dwelling-- women, as I said before, 10 women and three children, two children younger than I-- the lorry stopped in front of the place.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were loaded onto the place, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] strange people opposite me, sitting opposite.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There would be the Jews, turning in the eastern direction as the truck went along, trying to make contact with God.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were calling out, [NON ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "God was on holiday, so He never heard them, because they shot 17,000 Jews on that spot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You might ask, how do you talk to me now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were undressed like the rest with German perverted precision, precision.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to put [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] pants, our panties rather, and dresses, on different little heaps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were mountains of clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as soon as you undressed-- it might be a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] trivial detail, but the Poles who were assisting the Germans, they were there in a shot, looking through the seams of the clothing in case you buried something, you had something in it.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they would turn around to the Jews who were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shot, saying what do you bastards need this for?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't need anything any longer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the Polish comment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where was this spot?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This spot was called Lubianka, in the Lubianka Hills, outside Luck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I come to the miracle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Suddenly, in the shooting-- I call it the shooting gallery-- the volley of shots stopped for a second, and someone said, stop.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I looked up, and it was my biggest, my big brother's friend, a Polish doctor called Richard Ludwig.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
